    <p class="eyebrow">The sky broke at 2:22 PM...</p>
    <h1>PROPHECY: <span>The Omega War Chronicles</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-text">
      When Heaven, ancient gods, and unseen powers collide, one life becomes the center
      of a war that was written long before the world knew his name.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://a.co/d/0b1hRY4Y" target="_blank">Buy on Amazon</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/about">Meet the Author</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
