        </p>
        <a class="card-link" href="/characters/josiah">Read More</a>
      </article>

      <article class="card heaven-glow-card storm-glow-card">
        <h3>Set</h3>
        <p class="role">God of Storms</p>
        <p>
          A force of storm, power, and destruction whose presence shifts the atmosphere
          of every battlefield.
        </p>
        <a class="card-link" href="/characters/set">Read More</a>
      </article>

      <article class="card heaven-glow-card">
        <h3>Elijah</h3>
        <p class="role">Prophet of Thunder</p>
